title: Can I uninstall my carrier-customized or other preinstalled applications?
answer:
Preinstalled system applications cannot be uninstalled. Whether carrier-customized applications can be uninstalled depends on your carrier.   

On the All screen, touch Manage apps > All, select the application you want to uninstall, touch Uninstall, and follow the onscreen instructions to remove the application.   

If the Uninstall button is unavailable for an application, the application cannot be uninstalled.
